snippet.textDisplay:
I never bother with veal for my demi. I just back a brown beef stock and its absolutely delicious.
Any stock or broth and be frozen in ice cube trays for even portions. that can be stored in the trays or ziplock bags. I have both 1T and 1oz cubes and a large cube mold for cocktail ice that makes 3oz blocks. They are easy to use with a recipe or freehand and keep up to 6 months without a noticeable difference in flavor.
